{
  "title": "FinAgent — Evals",
  "uid": "finagent-evals",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": { "from": "now-24h", "to": "now" },
  "timezone": "browser",
  "tags": ["finagent", "eval"],
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Faithfulness",
      "description": "RAGAS: fraction of claims in the answer that are supported by retrieved context (1 = fully grounded)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0, "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red",    "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.6  },
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0.8  }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "finagent_eval_score{metric=\"faithfulness\"}",
          "legendFormat": "faithfulness",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Answer Relevancy",
      "description": "RAGAS: how relevant the answer is to the question (1 = fully relevant)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0, "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red",    "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.6  },
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0.8  }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "finagent_eval_score{metric=\"answer_relevancy\"}",
          "legendFormat": "answer_relevancy",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Context Precision",
      "description": "RAGAS: fraction of retrieved context that is relevant to the question",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0, "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red",    "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5  },
              { "color": "green",  "value": 0.75 }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "finagent_eval_score{metric=\"context_precision\"}",
          "legendFormat": "context_precision",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Hallucination Rate",
      "description": "LLM-judge: fraction of responses with groundedness < 0.6 (lower is better)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0, "max": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green",  "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.1  },
              { "color": "red",    "value": 0.3  }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "finagent_eval_score{metric=\"hallucination_rate\"}",
          "legendFormat": "hallucination_rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "All Eval Scores Over Time",
      "description": "Track faithfulness, relevancy, precision, recall and hallucination rate across eval runs",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "min": 0, "max": 1 }
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "right", "showLegend": true, "calcs": ["lastNotNull", "min", "max"] },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
          "expr": "finagent_eval_score",
          "legendFormat": "{{metric}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "How to run an eval",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Running an evaluation\n\nFrom the project root with the API running:\n\n```bash\n# All test cases\npython -m eval.runner\n\n# Specific tag\npython -m eval.runner --tag sanctions\npython -m eval.runner --tag hallucination_trap\n\n# Against a different API host\npython -m eval.runner --api http://localhost:8000\n```\n\n**Metrics explained**\n\n| Metric | Source | Good range |\n|---|---|---|\n| Faithfulness | RAGAS | > 0.8 |\n| Answer Relevancy | RAGAS | > 0.8 |\n| Context Precision | RAGAS | > 0.7 |\n| Context Recall | RAGAS | > 0.7 |\n| Hallucination Rate | LLM-judge | < 0.1 |"
      }
    }
  ]
}
